Package ohos.bluetooth.ble

Class BleAdvertiseData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.bluetooth.ble.BleAdvertiseData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public final class BleAdvertiseData
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Encapsulates the Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) advertising data, including the data to be advertised as well as the response data for active scans.

    You can use BleAdvertiseData.Builder to create a BleAdvertiseData instance.

    Since:
    3
    See Also:
